TableName: case when Discount_Tkt_Price='0.01' and Prod_ID='S01027' then 0.00

DatabaseName: end as Discount_Tkt_Price --一卡通员工卡，0.01为记次卡，0.00为

TableName: CASE WHEN Total_Score <= 0 THEN 0  --非折扣数据，默认值为0

DatabaseName: OR ((Theory_Tkt_Price*100)-(Discount_Tkt_Price*100)<> Period_Discount_Amt+Score_Discount_Amt ) then 1  --异常折扣数据，默认给1

TableName: CASE WHEN PROD_ID LIKE 'S010117%' AND Total_Score >0 AND  ((Theory_Tkt_Price*100)-(Discount_Tkt_Price*100)<> Period_Discount_Amt+Score_Discount_Amt )  AND Score_Discount_Amt>0

DatabaseName: OR ((Theory_Tkt_Price*100)-(Discount_Tkt_Price*100)<> Period_Discount_Amt+Score_Discount_Amt )  THEN	'100' --异常数据+非折扣数据
WHEN Period_Discount_Amt <= 0 THEN cast(cast((1-Score_Discount_Amt/(Theory_Tkt_Price*100))*100 as integer) as char(3))   --时段折扣为<=0时
END ) END Score_Discount_Cd 	  ----积分折扣代码
OR ((Theory_Tkt_Price*100)-(Discount_Tkt_Price*100)<> Period_Discount_Amt+Score_Discount_Amt )  THEN '100'  --一卡通异常不打折数据
